# bound to maximize: Key m W 2 Move
Key q WTSF 2 Close
Key k W 2 Destroy
AddToFunc StickAndStay
+ I Current Stick
+ I Current (Sticky) Layer 6
+ I Current (!Sticky) Layer default
Key s WTSF 2 StickAndStay
